title: 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Townhouse End Unit Townhome
posting_body: ['End Unit Two-level Townhouse in Prior Lake.', "Upstairs- Master bedroom (17'X12') with walk-in closet, laundry room, 2nd Bedroom, 1 Bath, kitchen with breakfast bar, family room, and maintenance free deck.", 'Downstairs- 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, and a second family room with walkout.', 'Brick exterior with maintenance-free vinyl siding.', 'Walkout basement to wetlands.', 'Two car attached garage.', 'This is a spacious home (1596 sq/ft) with many beautiful amenities.', 'Quick access to shopping and the major highways for an easy commute.', 'Home includes Central Air, Dishwasher, Washer, Dryer, water softener, and all general appliances.', 'Monthly Association Dues are included and paid by landlord.', 'Surrounding areas include Burnsville, Savage, Shakopee, and Lakeville.', 'Savage, Prior Lake School District.', 'Craig- call or text', 'show contact info', '.', 'No pets.', 'No smoking.', '2 year lease minimum.', '$1949/month includes HOA dues.', 'Trash removal included.', 'Snow removal included.', 'Lawn care included.', 'Sorry, I do not accept Section 8.', '$50 per adult application fee.', 'Available October 1st, 2022']
